data.description: Welcome to this stunning, newly constructed (2021) 2-story haven! This home boasts modern features throughout, including a spacious open-concept kitchen that seamlessly flows into a cozy den - perfect for entertaining or quiet evenings. Retreat to the main-level master suite featuring a full bath with a tub-shower combo and a spacious walk-in closet. The second story unveils a unique design with 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, as well as an expansive bonus room and loft area that acts as a secondary wing - offering exceptional privacy for its inhabitants.Indulge in the beauty of the outdoors from your screened-in porch, directly accessible from the den, or step into a meticulously landscaped fenced yard teeming with lush plants and greenery, creating a serene oasis right at home.Practical amenities include a downstairs laundry room with direct garage access, where you'll find a freshly painted space complete with both walls and floors. Guests will appreciate the conveniently located half-bath just off the foyer upon entry.  The home also comes with a stackable washer and dryer, a full double-door refrigerator, and window blinds throughout. The garage's polished aesthetics and the overall attention to detail in this home's design are evident at every turn.
